python-gridftp
============
A python wrapper for the c api of the globus library, gridftp section.


Installation
============
Requires globus gridftp-client library installation, with GLOBUS_LOCATION
set to the directory containing the installation.

To install:

    python setup.py build
    sudo python setup.py install


Usage
=====
from gridftpClient import gridftpwrapper


Building OS Packages
====================
To build debian Wheezy packages, do

  make deb

To build Centos 6.4 RPMs, do

  make rpm

  
Tests
=====  
Some simple tests are in the files named test_*. These are more
akin to minimal examples than tests, but better than nothing.
